==Gameplay Notes==
===Special Mechanics===
* Able to convert between Kai Ni and Kai Ni D.

'''Kai Ni'''
* Can equip seaplane bombers, seaplane fighters and autogyros.
* Can equip Aviation Personnel.

'''Kai Ni D'''
* Can equip landing craft, and tanks.
* Can equip [[:Category:Midget_Submarine|midget submarines]] and perform opening torpedo attacks.
* Loses ability to equip any seaplanes or torpedoes.

===Overview===
* High firepower, torpedo, and armor.
* Average ASW and HP.
* Small aircraft slot sizes for Seaplane Bombers.

